                        <h1 class="c-article-title" data-test="article-title" data-article-title="">On the utility of identification schemes for digital earth science data: an assessment and recommendations</h1>
                        <ul class="c-article-author-list c-article-author-list--short" data-test="authors-list" data-component-authors-activator="authors-list"><li class="c-article-author-list__item"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-label="link" href="#auth-Ruth_E_-Duerr" data-author-popup="auth-Ruth_E_-Duerr" data-corresp-id="c1">Ruth E. Duerr<svg width="16" height="16" focusable="false" role="img" aria-hidden="true" class="u-icon"><use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#global-icon-email"></use></svg></a><sup class="u-js-hide"><a href="#Aff1">1</a></sup>, </li><li class="c-article-author-list__item"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-label="link" href="#auth-Robert_R_-Downs" data-author-popup="auth-Robert_R_-Downs">Robert R. Downs</a><sup class="u-js-hide"><a href="#Aff2">2</a></sup>, </li><li class="c-article-author-list__item c-article-author-list__item--hide-small-screen"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-label="link" href="#auth-Curt-Tilmes" data-author-popup="auth-Curt-Tilmes">Curt Tilmes</a><sup class="u-js-hide"><a href="#Aff3">3</a></sup>, </li><li class="c-article-author-list__item c-article-author-list__item--hide-small-screen"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-label="link" href="#auth-Bruce-Barkstrom" data-author-popup="auth-Bruce-Barkstrom">Bruce Barkstrom</a><sup class="u-js-hide"><a href="#Aff6">6</a></sup>, </li><li class="c-article-author-list__item c-article-author-list__item--hide-small-screen"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-label="link" href="#auth-W__Christopher-Lenhardt" data-author-popup="auth-W__Christopher-Lenhardt">W. Christopher Lenhardt</a><sup class="u-js-hide"><a href="#Aff7">7</a></sup>, </li><li class="c-article-author-list__item c-article-